text: Võ Nhật Tân (born 27 June 1987) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a defender for V-League (Vietnam) club SHB Đà Nẵng. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:V.League 1 players Category:SHB Da Nang F.C. players Category:People from Tiền Giang Province
